structured_data.overview: The City of El Segundo Climate Action Plan is a tool to identify community-wide strategies to lower Greenhouse Gas (GHG) emissions across various sectors including transportation, land use, energy generation and consumption, water and waste.

documents.title: City of El Segundo Climate Action Plan
documents.description: The Climate Action Plan document for the City of El Segundo

structured_data.other_info: The Climate Action Plan aims to enhance the community environment, promote zero-emission vehicles, reduce energy and water usage in buildings, reduce waste, transform built environments into green spaces, and support renewable energy and storage markets.
